
== LYLAS (Internet Slang) ==


LYLAS stands for Love You Like A Sister.  You use this when you are talking on instant messenger. You can also use this slang when you are writing a letter or and e-mail to a friend or texting a friend.  You use LYLAS when you are talking to a girl friend that is so close to you that you feel as if they could be your sister.  It's something that you say to them when you are ending a conversation.  For example:


Girl Friend:  I've got to go, but I'll talk to you later!
You:  Ok! LYLAS!